  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Serena_Malyon_A_Rose_of_Gold.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/Serena_Malyon_A_Rose_of_Gold.jpg/350px-Serena_Malyon_A_Rose_of_Gold.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/Serena_Malyon_A_Rose_of_Gold.jpg/525px-Serena_Malyon_A_Rose_of_Gold.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/Serena_Malyon_A_Rose_of_Gold.jpg/700px-Serena_Malyon_A_Rose_of_Gold.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Serena_Malyon_A_Rose_of_Gold.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A Rose of Gold - by Serena Malyon © FFG</div></div></div>\n<p>\"<b>A Rose of Gold</b>\" is a song.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Rose_of_Gold&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Rose_of_Gold&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>It is sung by <a href=\"/index.php/Hamish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hamish\">Hamish the Harper</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Wedding\" title=\"Purple Wedding\">the wedding</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a> in honor of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Rose_of_Gold&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_60\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 60\">Chapter 60</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403225030\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 110/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 426/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 527/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.442      1 -total\n 75.47%    4.107      1 Template:Ref\n 47.15%    2.566      1 Template:Ref/c